non_residential_details.development_type: Change of Use with Extension(s) over 999sqm

description: Partial demolition, change of use, and erection of new build development to facilitate the provision of 204 residential units,  including 51 affordable housing units, 152 car parking spaces, of which 132 would be within a newly created basement, and 205 cycle parking spaces, together with associated landscape planting, access and servicing.  Conversion of library to restaurant and installation of associated extract ducting.
